<p><span class="katex-display"><span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>L</mi><mo>=</mo><msubsup><mtext mathvariant="bold">g</mtext><mi>R</mi><msub><mtext mathvariant="bold">a</mtext><mi>L</mi></msub></msubsup><mo>⋅</mo><msubsup><mtext mathvariant="bold">h</mtext><mi>L</mi><msub><mtext mathvariant="bold">b</mtext><mi>R</mi></msub></msubsup><mo>⋅</mo><msup><mi>u</mi><mrow><mo stretchy="false">⟨</mo><msub><mtext mathvariant="bold">a</mtext><mi>L</mi></msub><mo separator="true">,</mo><msub><mtext mathvariant="bold">b</mtext><mi>R</mi></msub><mo stretchy="false">⟩</mo></mrow></msup><mo separator="true">,</mo><mspace width="1em"></mspace><mi>R</mi><mo>=</mo><msubsup><mtext mathvariant="bold">g</mtext><mi>L</mi><msub><mtext mathvariant="bold">a</mtext><mi>R</mi></msub></msubsup><mo>⋅</mo><msubsup><mtext mathvariant="bold">h</mtext><mi>R</mi><msub><mtext mathvariant="bold">b</mtext><mi>L</mi></msub></msubsup><mo>⋅</mo><msup><mi>u</mi><mrow><mo stretchy="false">⟨</mo><msub><mtext mathvariant="bold">a</mtext><mi>R</mi></msub><mo separator="true">,</mo><msub><mtext mathvariant="bold">b</mtext><mi>L</mi></msub><mo stretchy="false">⟩</mo></mrow></msup><mi mathvariant="normal">.</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">
L = \textbf{g}_R^{\textbf{a}_L} \cdot \textbf{h}_L^{\textbf{b}_R} \cdot u^{\langle \textbf{a}_L, \textbf{b}_R\rangle}, \quad 
R = \textbf{g}_L^{\textbf{a}_R} \cdot \textbf{h}_R^{\textbf{b}_L} \cdot u^{\langle \textbf{a}_R, \textbf{b}_L\rangle}.
</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.68333em;vertical-align:0em;"></span><span class="mord mathdefault">L</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2777777777777778em;"></span><span class="mrel">=</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2777777777777778em;"></span></span><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:1.049744em;vertical-align:-0.293531em;"></span><span class="mord"><span class="mord text"><span class="mord textbf">g</span></span><span class="msupsub"><span class="vlist-t vlist-t2"><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.7562130000000001em;"><span style="top:-2.4064690000000004em;margin-right:0.05em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:2.7em;"></span><span class="sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight"><span class="mord mathdefault mtight" style="margin-right:0.00773em;">R</span></span></span><span style="top:-3.1451050000000005em;margin-right:0.05em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:2.7em;"></span><span class="sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight"><span class="mord mtight"><span class="mord mtight"><span class="mord text mtight"><span class="mord textbf mtight">a</span></span><span class="msupsub"><span class="vlist-t vlist-t2"><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.3448em;"><span style="top:-2.3567071428571427em;margin-right:0.07142857142857144em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:2.5em;"></span><span class="sizing reset-size3 size1 mtight"><span class="mord mathdefault mtight">L</span></span></span></span><span class="vlist-s">​</span></span><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.14329285714285717em;"><span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span class="vlist-s">​</span></span><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.293531em;"><span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.222222222